===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|almande|lang=fro}}, from [[Romance]] *{{term||amendla}} (with ''-l-'' in French and Spanish, probably by confusion with similar Arabic words), from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|amygdala|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἀμυγδάλη|sc=polytonic|lang=grc|tr=amugdala}}.

